{"tid":2372504,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無方法保養/清下肺","createTime":"2021-01-19T17:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T11:34:04.000Z","uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb94470dde0d1095b29372b9c35381d4e7045c0c","tid":2372504,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T17:07:09.000Z","msg":"工作原因<br />\n有時會吸入到啲揮發物同煙 （焊接既松香）<br />\n<br />\n以前無為意<br />\n因為吸到都好似無乜事<br />\n但慢慢愈來愈差<br />\n吸到少少都已經唔舒服 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家整左啲通風設備<br />\n但偶爾都會吸到啲啲<br />\n吸到少少已經好唔舒服 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肺好似有啲啲揪住咁<br />\n<br />\n但呼吸無問題<br />\n<br />\n希望邊位可以有啲良方<br />\n畀我救救個肺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n食煙人仕會唔會方法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n使唔使睇醫生/中醫果啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ae2c66a97f430d58a19ddd811d22559050eb78","tid":2372504,"uid":378999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T17:09:25.000Z","msg":"戴豬嘴做嘢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"663bf827dd0c862d8327f6bfe4866274f78b9f67","tid":2372504,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11ae2c66a97f430d58a19ddd811d22559050eb78","tid":2372504,"uid":378999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T17:09:25.000Z","msg":"戴豬嘴做嘢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-19T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"之後可能要長戴口罩做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗住做好抽風就得<br />\n但有時都會抽唔哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係戴罩做啦<br />\n洗呢啲錢好過去睇醫生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過就算以唔會再吸到<br />\n我都想救番個肺先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4259c2a7f0535cf7819d977cabee9a9bbe37ce17","tid":2372504,"uid":165956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:14:02.000Z","msg":"每日早晚用粗鹽溝煮滾過嘅暖水  用針筒洗鼻啦<br />\n跟住平時飲下枇杷膏清肺養肺  當個肺同氣管夠濕潤可以促進氣管黏液分泌  排走啲污糟野"},{"pid":"d6eef450db0817cb1d8ae62e30bd97de0a2bffd0","tid":2372504,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4259c2a7f0535cf7819d977cabee9a9bbe37ce17","tid":2372504,"uid":165956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T07:14:02.000Z","msg":"每日早晚用粗鹽溝煮滾過嘅暖水  用針筒洗鼻啦<br />\n跟住平時飲下枇杷膏清肺養肺  當個肺同氣管夠濕潤可以促進氣管黏液分泌  排走啲污糟野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T09:28:09.000Z","msg":"謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb03ae4b8c7d6ac9fb318830e4bc635960643ed9","tid":2372504,"uid":140337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"一定要帶豬嘴做嘢啦，真係幫你隔到好多，普通口罩跟本隔唔曬"},{"pid":"a0f6fc11b815ff32c4fb86a47c7f65d10d92de60","tid":2372504,"uid":262674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb03ae4b8c7d6ac9fb318830e4bc635960643ed9","tid":2372504,"uid":140337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"一定要帶豬嘴做嘢啦，真係幫你隔到好多，普通口罩跟本隔唔曬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"以後會帶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家係想清番好個肺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"917d80fd0499eff0a939d95cb82b361684c5d99a","tid":2372504,"uid":176121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f6fc11b815ff32c4fb86a47c7f65d10d92de60","tid":2372504,"uid":262674,"li